block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: This is Paper plane 24 of our 100 Exotic Paper Airplane Challenge. The Shuttlecock designed by Michael G. LaFosse. This one flies really straight. This is an origami plane folded from a square sheet. Enjoy!!! If you missed my last Exotic Paper Airplane "Paper Plane 023 : Chuck Finn by Michael G. LaFosse", you could watch it at https://youtu.be/_5ioFyaVjY4 Thanks for watching! Wilson Lee @Heap Art
